name: If Pigeons had Hands (Halloween Collector Special)
description:
He has levitated straight from Transylvania Castle, to join you on Halloween Night. It's Dracula himself, with two of his minions. 

Holding a glass of... wine. 
He doesn't walk, or bop. He levitates, gently enough not to spill his wine. 

Enjoy his presence. 

This is an exclusive Pigeon given to holders of 3 or more Halloween pigeons.
